<p>Hello <%= studentName %>,</p>
<p>Your question in the course <strong><%= courseTitle %></strong> has been answered!</p>
<div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Your Question:</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 15px 0;"><em>"<%= question %>"</em></p>
    <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Instructor Reply:</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0;"><strong>"<%= reply %>"</strong></p>
</div>
<p>Log in to your dashboard to view the full discussion and continue learning.</p>
